text:
Preliminary Findings of #mRNA #Covid19 #Vaccine Safety in #Pregnant Persons

827 of v-safe pregnancy participants had a completed pregnancy:
13.9% resulted in a pregnancy loss
86.1% resulted in a live birth
Findings did not show obvious safety signals.
